## Optimization Suggestions

Suggest optimizations proactively when reviewing or repairing a workflow:

| Pattern to flag | Better approach |
|---|---|
| More than 8 steps for a simple task | Consolidate action nodes |
| Branching without error path | Add explicit error/fallback branch |
| Notification-only workflow with no data check | Add a condition node before sending |
| Polling trigger on short intervals (< 5 min) | Suggest webhook trigger if available |
| Multiple HTTP calls to the same API | Batch into one call with filters |
| No failure notification | Add a channel node on the error branch |

